snippet: Lindsey Vonn won her 13th World Cup event in Lake Louise, Alberta, in another 1-2 United States finish in the second downhill there this weekend.
abstract: Lindsey Vonn captures the downhill in Lake Louise, Alberta, for her 13th World Cup win this season.
